INCIPIT grimoire "bitwise_all"

RITUALE main() REDDE REX
  EVOCA REX a AD 60
  EVOCA REX b AD 13
  EVOCA REX r1 AD a ET_BIT b
  EVOCA REX r2 AD a VEL_BIT b
  EVOCA REX r3 AD a XOR b
  EVOCA REX r4 AD a SINISTER 2
  EVOCA REX r5 AD a DEXTER 2
  EVOCA REX r6 AD NON_BIT b
  EVOCA REX soma AD r1 + r2 + r3 + r4 + r5
  REDDE soma
EXPLICIT RITUALE

EXPLICIT grimoire
